	<h1 class="title">“SPORT”背后，本田如何一步步展现它的运动“基因”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name"></span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-23 23:39:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/27015/medium/27015.JPG?1463561008" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


